name: The King's Dreams: Warriors Call
description:
The elders called a Grandmasters meeting. The time had come to search for new lands.
The tribe was expanding. Mothers required new homes to raise their young. Young men had taken on wives and needed new lands to raise their own families.
This King was ready.
He did not know yet but he would indeed be leading them to a new place.
Time had been taken.
The inspiration had arrived.
The space was now free.
The future was beamed into the minds of those that knew.
The ignorance would never succeed.
Their emotional intelligence was now their sword from here to beyond.
